        "content": "<p>I start to learn rfl and try the rust_out_of_tree example base on rust-next branch, but when add this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">workqueue</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">system_long</span><span class=\"p\">().</span><span class=\"n\">try_spawn</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">GFP_KERNEL</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">||</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">pr_info</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"hello world!\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"p\">})</span><span class=\"o\">?</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>it compile error:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Bash\"><pre><span></span><code>@JCKeep<span class=\"w\"> </span>➜<span class=\"w\"> </span>/workspaces/rust-out-of-tree<span class=\"w\"> </span>$<span class=\"w\"> </span>make<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LLVM</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">KDIR</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>../linux\nmake<span class=\"w\"> </span>-C<span class=\"w\"> </span>../linux<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">M</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"nv\">$PWD</span>\nmake<span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>Entering<span class=\"w\"> </span>directory<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">'/workspaces/linux'</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>RUSTC<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>M<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>/workspaces/rust-out-of-tree/rust_out_of_tree.o\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>MODPOST<span class=\"w\"> </span>/workspaces/rust-out-of-tree/Module.symvers\nERROR:<span class=\"w\"> </span>modpost:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"_RNvNCNvMs0_NtCsgd4OX6xQzCQ_6kernel9workqueueNtB9_5Queue9try_spawns_05CLASS\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>/workspaces/rust-out-of-tree/rust_out_of_tree.ko<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>undefined!\nmake<span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>***<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>scripts/Makefile.modpost:145:<span class=\"w\"> </span>/workspaces/rust-out-of-tree/Module.symvers<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Error<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1</span>\nmake<span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>***<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>/workspaces/linux/Makefile:1877:<span class=\"w\"> </span>modpost<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Error<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2</span>\nmake<span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>***<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>Makefile:224:<span class=\"w\"> </span>__sub-make<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Error<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2</span>\nmake<span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>Leaving<span class=\"w\"> </span>directory<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">'/workspaces/linux'</span>\nmake:<span class=\"w\"> </span>***<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>Makefile:6:<span class=\"w\"> </span>default<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Error<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>source file:<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/7c1SzIdDYFrzazcEcIqMxpC0/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"